sources.title: Cowboys Don't Cry - Full Movie
sources.description:
In this family drama, Josh is a veteran rodeo cowboy who must care for his young son Shane after the death of his wife Lucy. The two move to the ranch left to them by Shane's grandfather, but Josh can't hold a job, and Shane is in the throes of adolescent angst. Lindsay, their neighbor and a veterinarian, tends to Shane's injured horse and the emotional wounds of the father and son.
